==English==

===Noun===
{{en-verb|interlac|ing}}

# {{transitive}} To [[cross]] one with another; to [[interweave]]: as, to interlace wires; hence, to [[mingle]]; to [[blend]].
# {{intransitive}} To cross one another as if [[weave|woven]] together, as interlacing branches; to [[intertwine]]; to blend [[intricately]].

